title: ‘Duck Dynasty’ Star Si to Appear at Oldham Chemicals PestWorld Booth
text:
Subscribe ‘Duck Dynasty’ Star Si to Appear at Oldham Chemicals PestWorld Booth Oldham Chemicals Company invites PestWorld '15 attenddees to its booth (#441) to meet Si Robertson, one of the stars of the reality television program "Duck Dynasty." October 15, 2015 Oldham Chemicals Company invites PestWorld '15 attenddees to its booth (#441) to meet Si Robertson, one of the stars of the reality television program "Duck Dynasty." A professional photographer will be on hand for attendees to get their picture taken with Si. Additionally, there will be drawings with autographed items with Duck Dynasty merchandise. Si will be at the Oldham booth (#441) on Oct. 20, at 2:30 p.m. Related Expanded Label for Contrac All-Weather Blox October 16, 2015
